title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 26 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 26 2022
description:
Joe Biden speaking is never a good thing: accuses Trump and Republicans of "semi-fascism." New York Governor Kathy Hochul’s call for 5.4M Republicans to leave New York is dangerous and disgusting. Mark Zuckerberg: FBI pushed Facebook to crack down on misinformation before Hunter Biden laptop story was published. So, the FBI intentionally helped rig the election for Joe Biden by covering for Hunter Biden’s laptop before the 2020 election and is now raiding the house of Donald Trump, his most likely upcoming opponent. Seems like the FBI might be the actual threat to democracy here. Heavily redacted Mar-a-Largo affidavit finally released. Clay and Buck note that the documents are so "top secret" that the National Archives wanted them Fed-Ex'd.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
